    "description": "你想要建立一个兔兔天堂吗？踏上《Usagi Shima》充满兔兔的历险，动手将废弃小岛改造成可爱兔兔们的温馨避风港！《Usagi Shima》是一款轻松愉快的兔兔收集休闲游戏。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144010/extras/cb7cfd306e67556ad4a4ef43a7895c29.webp?t=1771552016\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br>将你的小岛改造成异想天开，充满玩具、花草植物和华丽建筑装饰的兔兔天堂。放松并同步享受一天中属于你的宁静温馨的小岛氛围～<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144010/extras/7905912dd650f14e790b9717ae21f4a7.poster.avif?t=1771552016\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144010/extras/7905912dd650f14e790b9717ae21f4a7.webm?t=1771552016\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144010/extras/7905912dd650f14e790b9717ae21f4a7.mp4?t=1771552016\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144010/extras/e8448c1995591fac2d6bb22b60bc24f2.webp?t=1771552016\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br>在你的岛屿上用可爱的装饰来吸引毛茸茸的游客，并与可爱的兔兔成为朋友。帮它们戴上亮眼的帽子，让你成为兔兔的最佳伙伴并赢得特别的礼物！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144010/extras/405d2a02398ec86a7eaab85c53b32ebb.poster.avif?t=1771552016\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144010/extras/405d2a02398ec86a7eaab85c53b32ebb.webm?t=1771552016\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144010/extras/405d2a02398ec86a7eaab85c53b32ebb.mp4?t=1771552016\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144010/extras/8e9085bf33296bd9bffeeb3c29bb060b.webp?t=1771552016\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br>在对的时机，遇见稀有的特殊兔兔来拜访你的小岛。看看你能不能遇到并收集所有兔兔！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144010/extras/9e0737af817efc7d6911433b19927d55.poster.avif?t=1771552016\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144010/extras/9e0737af817efc7d6911433b19927d55.webm?t=1771552016\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144010/extras/9e0737af817efc7d6911433b19927d55.mp4?t=1771552016\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144010/extras/6e30262856b4dab7e836db3fce341e4f.webp?t=1771552016\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br>用拍照功能，捕捉你与兔兔伙伴们的可爱回忆。创作一本充满温馨时刻的剪贴簿，甚至将这些照片保存到您的设备中作为桌面壁纸！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144010/extras/c5283bf43a31beac75ae63e97614dbc3.webp?t=1771552016\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br>向你的兔兔们展现满满的爱！喂食它们，梳理蓬松的毛，并进行好玩的活动。在你对兔兔伙伴们展现爱意时，看看它们开心的模样。让自己沉浸在温馨的气氛里，与您的兔兔朋友们一起度过珍贵的时光。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144010/extras/b9af63751210c625b10fcc7779211b09.webp?t=1771552016\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br>设计可爱的商店和美丽的景色，创作一个独一无二的兔兔度假村。设计一个迷人的仙境，为充满兔兔的岛屿增添魅力。<br><br>准备好放松身心，在《Usagi Shima》创造一个令人愉悦的兔兔仙境！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144010/extras/6f22352ffe101bcf2e62ffcb865d3ebe.poster.avif?t=1771552016\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144010/extras/6f22352ffe101bcf2e62ffcb865d3ebe.webm?t=1771552016\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144010/extras/6f22352ffe101bcf2e62ffcb865d3ebe.mp4?t=1771552016\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144010/extras/e9cef43ea9957de1a8e93173cb7aef79.webp?t=1771552016\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>发现并收集超过 30 种独特外观和特色的兔兔！<br></li><li>收集超过 100 种装饰品，有些甚至可以进行互动！<br></li><li>摸摸、喂食、梳毛，并和兔兔玩躲猫猫来巩固友谊<br></li><li>用可爱的帽子打扮你的兔兔！<br></li><li>从你最要好的兔兔朋友收到纪念品，甚至邀请它们留在你的岛上。<br></li><li>拍摄快照建立可爱的相册，甚至将拍摄的照片制作为设备的桌面壁纸<br></li><li>手绘传统动画艺术风格<br></li><li>与现实时间同步，体验与您的日程符合的岛屿氛围 <br></li><li>温馨的休闲游戏体验：无时间限制、无压力、按照您的步调悠哉的游玩！</li></ul><br>快来玩《Usagi Shima》……<br><br>如果你对兔兔没有抵抗力、梦想拥有兔兔的陪伴，或者你是一位骄傲的兔兔家长，《Usagi Shima》就是你的完美游戏！跃入一个充满可爱兔兔的宁静世界，体验悠哉愉快的游玩。<br><br>如果你热爱布置、室内设计、经营游戏、点击式游戏和模拟游戏，或者你喜爱如《动物森友会》、《星露谷物语》、《Cats &amp; Soup》、《猫咪收集》这类的放松的游戏和其他口袋露营游戏。<br><br>如果你在找寻放松、冥想，以及释放焦虑和忧郁的方式，并沉迷于可爱的游戏和迷人的艺术的话，《Usagi Shima》就是你的首选。<br><br>快踏上《Usagi Shima》的奇幻旅程，兔兔天堂等着带给你丰富的喜悦！",
